Invocation Name: cisco certified network associate quiz
des:
Test your knowledge in preparation for the CCNA (Cisco Certified Network Associate) exam. 

This Cisco Certified Network Associate Quiz is that allows you to help you acquire information that will help you pass CCNA

Disclaimer: This Cisco Certified Network Associate Quiz app is not associated with Cisco organisation and CCNA is a trademark of Cisco duly acknowledged.

Available commands

To start, just say "Alexa, open cisco certified network associate quiz " 
5 posible multiple choice questions
You can answer the following ways, Respond with the number of the answer. 1 | 2 | 3 | 4 | 5
To repeat the last question, say, repeat
To start a new game at any time, say, start game
To cancel or end a quiz, say, cancel or end
To get help, say, Help
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
